        <content><![CDATA[    <h1 class="title topictitle1">Create, modify, or delete a welcome page section</h1>        <div class="body taskbody">       <ul class="ul steps-unordered"><li class="li step">                <span class="ph cmd">To create or modify a welcome page section:</span>                <ol class="ol substeps" id="sys_home-setup__substeps_u5b_mfz_bv"><li class="li substep substepexpand">                        <span class="ph cmd">Enter or modify the <span class="ph uicontrol">Short description</span>.</span>                    </li><li class="li substep substepexpand">                        <span class="ph cmd">In the <span class="ph uicontrol">Condition</span> field, enter the                                following:gs.getUser().getCompanyRecord().name.toString()                                &#61;&#61; &#34;Company&#34;</span>                        <div class="itemgroup info"><em class="ph i">Company</em> is the name of your company.</div>                    </li><li class="li substep substepexpand">                        <span class="ph cmd">Complete or modify the other fields in the form as needed.</span>                    </li><li class="li substep substepexpand">                        <span class="ph cmd">Click <span class="ph uicontrol">Submit</span> or                            <span class="ph uicontrol">Update</span>.</span>                    </li></ol>            </li><li class="li step">                <span class="ph cmd">To delete a section, click <span class="ph uicontrol">Delete</span>.</span>            </li></ul>    </div>    <div class="related-links"><div class="relinfo"><div class="reltitle">Related information<br /><div><a class="link" href="https://docs.servicenow.com/?context&#61;CSHelp:Create-Welcome-Page-Section&amp;version&#61;kingston" target="_blank">Create welcome page section</a></div></div></div></div>]]></content>
